ğŸ›  Tools Used

FastRecon integrates trusted open-source tools commonly used in security operations:

assetfinder â€“ Subdomain discovery

netcat (nc) â€“ Lightweight connectivity checks

nmap â€“ Port scanning

gowitness â€“ Web screenshotting

nuclei â€“ Template-based vulnerability detection

Each tool is used in a non-intrusive, read-only manner.

